<!--T:4-->
The [[Image:Curves_ZebraTool.svg|24px]] [[Curves_ZebraTool|Curves ZebraTool]] tool creates a Zebra texture for surface inspection.

==Usage== <!--T:5-->

<!--T:6-->
# Select the surface to be tested
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the [[Image:Curves_ZebraTool.svg|24px]] [[Curves_ZebraTool|Zebra texture for surface inspection]] button
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Surfaces → Zebra Tool}} option from the menu
# Change the Zebra Tool parameter to the required conditions

==Properties== <!--T:9-->

<!--T:12-->
* {{PropertyData|Black Stripes Width}}: Change the black stripes width.
* {{PropertyData|Scale}}: Scale the Zebra stripes.
* {{PropertyData|Rotation}}: Rotate the Zebra stripes.

